{"tid":209992,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"好多謝老公將我地拉返埋一齊。。。","createTime":"2017-04-20T15:36:47.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-20T15:50:44.000Z","uid":277,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"31faf91cb27b37cce476807e2899c2d7e20a36e9","tid":209992,"uid":277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T15:36:47.000Z","msg":"同老公拍拖三年結婚四年 冇小朋友 生活平淡到嘔..<br />\n最近識左個男仔 係細過我 但談吐舉止都好成熟 約過我幾次出街 雖然我心郁郁 但都拒絕左..<br />\n上個禮拜同老公週年紀念 佢冇book餐廳冇送禮物 我心唸一早估到 亦都冇抱任何期望<br />\n收工返到屋企 老公話佢買左套戲叫我同佢一齊睇(心唸點解而家仲會有人買碟睇戲..)<br />\n點知電視mon見到既係我地一齊甘耐(尤其是拍拖期間)拍低既片..<br />\n我既第一次生日..佢既第一次生日..我地第一次去旅遊..同埋當年去歐洲玩skydiving之後佢摞隻戒指出黎求婚..<br />\n老公乜都冇講..但我唔知點解突然喊到隻狗咁..<br />\n其實愛情一直都系我地之間..不過係我唔明白細水長流既道理..忽略左老公平時對我既細心體貼<br />\n係個一刻.我明白自己最應該做d咩...<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc8860e3c94c02a81b31c1cee20a019a6e80d1df","tid":209992,"uid":85586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T15:37:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://beautyexchange.com.hk/forum.php?mod=viewthread&amp;tid=729177\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbeautyexchange.com.hk%2Fforum.php%3Fmod%3Dviewthread%26tid%3D729177&d=68p4wiGQQ1h%2Fwz3iobjDK9r9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=fdc4ba56\" target=\"_blank\">http://beautyexchange.com.hk/forum.php?mod=viewthread&amp;tid=729177</a>"},{"pid":"ecc3feff1f4064c75dc991c95df7f64ea9988292","tid":209992,"uid":13088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T15:38:04.000Z","msg":"樓主掛住你"},{"pid":"5c70fe6fa5fbc62c7935906f770115ded8e9fd71","tid":209992,"uid":277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T15:38:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主掛住你</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/13.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5366c5785d77c3337b18f47b03df018575c8905","tid":209992,"uid":277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T15:39:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"http://beautyexchange.com.hk/forum.php?mod=viewthread&amp;tid=729177\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbeautyexchange.com.hk%2Fforum.php%3Fmod%3Dviewthread%26tid%3D729177&d=68p4wiGQQ1h%2Fwz3iobjDK9r9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=fdc4ba56\" target=\"_blank\">http://beautyexchange.com.hk/forum.php?mod=viewthread&amp;tid=729177</a></blockquote><br />\nshy shy牙<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64ecd079916568780ae78a1df7166b83bea85081","tid":209992,"uid":5487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T15:40:26.000Z","msg":"有時拍拖耐咗結婚耐咗<br />\n需要新鮮感嘅都唔一定係男人先會<br />\n<br />\n好多時女人對感情耐咗嘅時候，對待男人仲冷淡過乜咁<br />\n但係女方又唔覺得係咩問題<br />\n<br />\n無論係拍拖定結咗婚<br />\n雙方不忘製造下驚喜俾對方<br />\n咁就會好幸福"},{"pid":"024988ea7a16f9872fb177ac491b2f2dad255fe4","tid":209992,"uid":30922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T15:41:35.000Z","msg":"有洋蔥嘅....<br />\n好sweet呀ㅠㅠ"},{"pid":"3ce8b297cee23a83135011e061dcae5b340d1545","tid":209992,"uid":277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T15:42:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有時拍拖耐咗結婚耐咗<br />\n需要新鮮感嘅都唔一定係男人先會<br />\n<br />\n好多時女人對感情耐咗嘅時候，對待男人仲冷淡過乜咁<br />\n但係女方又唔覺得係咩問題<br />\n<br />\n無論係拍拖定結咗婚<br />\n雙方不忘製造下驚喜俾對方<br />\n咁就會好幸福</blockquote><br />\n係..唸翻自己一開始既唔識珍惜真係好蠢..<br />\n佢特登帶我去歐洲陪我玩skydiving(佢係一個連過山車都唔多敢玩既人)..岩岩落地我人都未企穩就見到佢單膝跪地求婚..唸翻真係好sweet<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/12.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/07.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9bf96f4ad330d75e900c41ca3ef5005c4130f2b5","tid":209992,"uid":277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T15:43:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有洋蔥嘅....<br />\n好sweet呀ㅠㅠ</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/2